# Changelog

## v0.2.0 (2026-03-19)

### Enhancements

- [Proxy] Add `User-Agent` and `Proxy-Connection: Keep-Alive` headers to upstream CONNECT requests, matching real client behavior
- [Proxy] Add per-rule `dns` field â€” custom DNS servers used only for connections matching that rule, without touching system DNS settings
- [Proxy] Add automatic auth scheme negotiation via `proxyplease` â€” transparently handles Basic, NTLM, and Negotiate per-connection by inspecting `Proxy-Authenticate` on 407 responses
- [Config] Add `upstream_domain` field for Active Directory NTLM auth â€” keeps the upstream URL clean and parseable
- [Router] Log collapsed to single line per request â€” host shown only on rule match


### Bug fixes

- [Proxy] Fix recurring 407 Proxy Authentication Required after ~45 minutes â€” upstream switches from Basic to Negotiate on session expiry, now handled transparently
- [Proxy] Fix hang on CONNECT when upstream requires NTLM and domain is not provided
- [Proxy] Fix upstream URL parsing failure with `domain\user` or `domain/user` format in credentials
- [Proxy] Fix 407 authentication failures caused by missing `Proxy-Connection: Keep-Alive` header in CONNECT tunnel

---

## v0.1.5 (2026-03-19)

### Enhancements

- [Proxy] Add per-rule `dns` field â€” custom DNS servers used only for connections matching that rule, without touching system DNS settings
- [Proxy] Add comprehensive logging to all proxy error paths â€” 502 failures now include the exact reason
- [Config] Introduce `Decision` type returned by `Decide()`, carrying both action and DNS servers
- [Router] Add deduplicating logger â€” repeated identical entries are suppressed and summarized every 100 occurrences
- [Network] Add 250ms debounce and same-value guard to `networkDidChange` to coalesce rapid network events
- [Network] Move SSID cache seeding from `init()` to `StartNetworkListener()` â€” binary startup is now side-effect free for subcommands like `completion`, `version`, `help`
- [CLI] Add `unknown command` error for unrecognized subcommands instead of silently falling back to `run`
- [CLI] Redact upstream proxy password in logs using `url.Redacted()`

### Bug fixes

- [Proxy] Fix 502 errors caused by upstream proxy hostname DNS resolution failures on network switch
- [Network] Fix SSID change event firing twice per network transition due to duplicate `SCDynamicStore` key registration
- [Completion] Fix `completion bash` exiting with code 1 during Homebrew install due to `init()` side effects

---

## v0.1.4 (2026-03-19)

### Enhancements

- [CI] Package darwin-arm64 binary as `.tar.gz` archive instead of bare binary
- [CI] Update release asset and Homebrew formula URL to use archive

### Bug fixes

- [Formula] Fix Homebrew install failure caused by bare binary URL â€” Homebrew requires an archive format

---

## v0.1.3 (2026-03-18)

### Enhancements

- [Formula] Streamline shell completion generation and config file creation in Homebrew formula
- [Network] Improve network listener initialization â€” `SCDynamicStore` setup is now deferred to `StartNetworkListener()`

### Bug fixes

- [CI] Fix Homebrew tap push authentication using explicit token URL in `git push`

---

## v0.1.2 (2026-03-18)

### Bug fixes

- [Formula] Fix shell completion installation path in Homebrew formula using `buildpath`
- [Formula] Move `zap` stanza outside `caveats` block

---

## v0.1.1 (2026-03-18)

### Enhancements

- [Formula] Install shell completions to Homebrew global completions directories during `brew install`

---

## v0.1.0 (2026-03-18)

### Enhancements

- [Formula] Add `zap` stanza to Homebrew formula to remove config and log files on uninstall
- [Install] Auto-install shell completions for bash, zsh, and fish during `proxy-router install`
- [CI] Auto-update Homebrew tap formula on release â€” computes sha256 and pushes updated formula
- [Brew] Add Homebrew formula with `brew services` support and `post_install` config generation
- [CI] Add GitHub Actions pipeline â€” build on `macos-14`, release on tag, auto-update tap
- [CLI] Add shell completions for zsh, bash, and fish via `proxy-router completion <shell>`
- [CLI] Add `install` / `uninstall` commands with LaunchAgent support and auto-detected install prefix
- [CLI] Add `-listen` flag on `run` to override listen address for local dev
- [Proxy] Add Basic auth support for authenticated upstream proxies (`http://user:pass@host:port`)
- [Proxy] Initial implementation â€” HTTP and HTTPS (`CONNECT`) proxying with rule-based routing
- [Router] Rule matching on SSID, domain suffix, and IP with AND logic
- [Router] Hot config reload â€” file watched for changes (1s poll) and on `SIGHUP`
- [Network] macOS network change listener via `SCDynamicStore` â€” SSID cache updated on network events with zero per-request shell-outs
- [Network] Correct Wi-Fi SSID detection via `ipconfig getsummary` for macOS 15.x compatibility
